snippet.title: 4 Nin Uchi Mahjong, Super Famicom
snippet.description:
4 Nin Uchi Mahjong was captured with Silver Crest video grabber and CyberLink PowerDirector 12 

https://www.lidl.de/de/silvercrest-usb-video-grabber-svg-2-0-a3/p253451

 Forever Games of NES 405 in 1 Multicart, #004 4 Nin Uchi Mahjong

https://ebay.to/2N2yBvH 

RetroPort NES to SNES Cartridge Adapter

 https://ebay.to/2SnmaR3

 Note: The video quality is significantly reduced in the captured gameplay. Playing the game without capture looks as it should on the NES using a composite cable.
